        <field>GuidanceText__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &apos;Segoe UI&apos;, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; margin: -8px -8px 16px -8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;margin: 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;üìù Update Record&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.95;&quot;&gt;Modify existing Salesforce records with automatic field-level security&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;font-size: 15px; color: #212529; margin: 16px 0 8px 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef; padding-bottom: 4px;&quot;&gt;üìã Runtime Parameters&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6c757d;&quot;&gt;The AI will provide these parameters when calling this action:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;background: white; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; margin: 12px 0;&quot;&gt;&lt;table style=&quot;width: 100%; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; width: 30%;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: #495057;&quot;&gt;recordId&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px; color: #dc3545;&quot;&gt;Required&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; color: #6c757d;&quot;&gt;The 18-character Salesforce ID of the record to update. 15-character IDs are automatically converted.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;background: #f1f3f5; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;&quot;001xxxxxxxxxxxxxxx&quot;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;padding: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: #495057;&quot;&gt;recordData&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px; color: #dc3545;&quot;&gt;Required&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;padding: 8px; color: #6c757d;&quot;&gt;JSON object containing field API names and their new values. Only include fields you want to update.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;background: #f1f3f5; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;{ &quot;Status&quot;: &quot;Closed&quot;, &quot;Priority&quot;: &quot;High&quot; }&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;font-size: 15px; color: #212529; margin: 16px 0 8px 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef; padding-bottom: 4px;&quot;&gt;‚öôÔ∏è Configuration Options&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;background: white; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; margin: 12px 0;&quot;&gt;&lt;table style=&quot;width: 100%; font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;padding: 8px; width: 30%;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: #495057;&quot;&gt;objectApiName&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11px; color: #6c757d;&quot;&gt;Optional&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;padding: 8px; color: #6c757d;&quot;&gt;When specified, validates that the recordId matches this object type. Useful for type safety in specific scenarios.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;background: #f1f3f5; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 11px;&quot;&gt;&quot;Case&quot;, &quot;Account&quot;, &quot;CustomObject__c&quot;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;background: #e7f1ff; border-left: 4px solid #0066cc; padding: 12px; margin: 12px 0; border-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #004085;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;üí° Note:&lt;/strong&gt; Field-level security is automatically enforced. Non-updateable fields are silently skipped. Validation rules fire normally and errors are returned to the AI.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</value>
